- A rat done bit my sister
Nell with whitey on the Moon.

52:14.458 --> 52:16.500
Her face and arms
began to swell,

52:16.583 --> 52:18.750
and whitey's on the Moon.

52:18.834 --> 52:22.917
I can't pay no doctor bills,
but whitey's on the Moon.

52:23.000 --> 52:24.959
Ten years from now,
I'll be paying still,

52:25.041 --> 52:26.583
while whitey's on the Moon.

52:26.667 --> 52:29.583
You know, the man just upped
my rent last night,

52:29.667 --> 52:31.291
'cause whitey's on the Moon.

52:31.375 --> 52:33.333
No hot water,
no toilets, no lights,

52:33.417 --> 52:35.625
but whitey's on the Moon.

52:35.709 --> 52:37.625
I wonder why he's upping me.

52:37.709 --> 52:39.583
'Cause whitey's on the Moon?

52:39.667 --> 52:41.750
Why, I was already
giving him 50 a week,

52:41.834 --> 52:44.041
and now whitey's on the Moon.

52:44.125 --> 52:46.166
Taxes taking
my whole damn check,

52:46.250 --> 52:48.125
the junkies
make me a nervous wreck,

52:48.208 --> 52:50.208
the price of food is going up,

52:50.291 --> 52:52.625
and as if all that crap
wasn't enough,

52:52.709 --> 52:56.834
a rat done bit my sister Nell,
with whitey on the Moon.

52:56.917 --> 52:58.959
Her face and arms
began to swell,

52:59.041 --> 53:01.083
and whitey's on the Moon.

53:01.166 --> 53:03.500
Was all that money
I made last year

53:03.583 --> 53:05.083
for whitey on the Moon?

53:05.166 --> 53:06.709
How come I ain't
got no money here?

53:06.792 --> 53:09.166
Hmm, whitey's on the Moon.

53:09.250 --> 53:13.667
You know, I just about had
my fill of whitey on the Moon.

53:13.750 --> 53:15.667
I think I'll send
these doctor bills,

53:15.750 --> 53:18.834
air mail special...

53:18.917 --> 53:21.875
[drum music]

53:21.959 --> 53:25.041
♪ ♪

53:25.125 --> 53:26.834
To whitey on the Moon.

53:26.917 --> 53:28.709
- [ominous chanting]

53:28.792 --> 53:32.125
[wind howling]

53:34.250 --> 53:38.667
[ominous chanting]

53:44.792 --> 53:49.667
[panting and grunting]

53:49.750 --> 53:51.500
- It's open!
Come on, come on!

53:51.583 --> 53:52.875
- If we move him,
he could bleed out!

53:52.959 --> 53:55.583
- Gotta get away!
- Go!

53:55.667 --> 53:58.417
[intense music]

53:58.500 --> 53:59.959
♪ ♪

